Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.89,0:02:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ruu-chan, you'll be late if you don't leave for school now, won't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.23,0:02:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh no!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.23,0:02:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll do the rest of the dishes.
