Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Ruu!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Tama.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it school time already?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a sleepy-head, Tama.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.76,0:03:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My, you're alone today? Where's Yuzuki-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, um, nothing... {## funi-line and i dig it, his betsuni/nothing is appropriately confusing/confused}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Akira still missing?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.65,0:03:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. A girl from her school said so.\NShe hasn't gone home at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been a week or so, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruu, the train's going to go! Ruu?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.36,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right, we're...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.20,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's not be friends anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're not friends anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't battle anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.87,0:04:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Yuzuki won't stop battling until her wish comes true.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what we decided.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.05,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... that's what we decided.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You serious?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the Kurebayashis in second year...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.23,0:04:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the twins?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard they're dating even though they're brother and sister!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't that ince—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, so the rumor is true?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Think they did it already?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.61,0:05:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they {\i1}do{\i0} live together.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault, Honoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.95,0:05:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You really shouldn't worry about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought he was cool...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you spread it to everyone?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.30,0:05:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault for doing something people would talk about.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.39,0:05:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All I said was that you were acting strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I just asked what everyone thought...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.52,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Honoka was worried about you, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.19,0:05:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt sorry that you and Yuzuki-san were being misunderstood.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.65,0:05:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what you want about me, but I won't\Nforgive anyone who insults Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.16,0:05:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You won't forgive me? That's awful!{## bit of a leap here to have her relate that to herself (Funi: C-Can't forgive...? That's so mean!); i figured it's not the pompous notion of forgiveness that's making her mad (it's all a bit more common in japanese anyway), but the realization that she fucked up, making her turn on him in a true act of being 16yo}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the worst...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.29,0:05:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why everyone is saying\Nyou two are getting it on and stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.58,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize to her!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a total loser.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.08,0:05:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your own fault anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they brother and sister?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}told{\i0} you it's crazy!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I feel bad thinking she was cute...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.57,0:06:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you told the others not to insult me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.61,0:06:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.61,0:06:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes me happy. But you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it {\i1}is{\i0} true.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.75,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,love you, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.75,0:06:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've loved you ever since we were kids.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.30,0:06:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I believed telling you that would make you hate me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.68,0:06:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought for the longest time.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goto-kun in class two, I guess...?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You really think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.27,0:07:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As I got older, all the girls\Naround me had boys they liked.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Yuzuki, how about you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.61,0:07:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We all said who we liked,\Nso now it's your turn!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who do you like?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.62,0:07:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I'm not really interested in boys...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aww, you're lying!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.17,0:07:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's true! There's totally no one I like.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.67,0:07:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're {\i0}lying{\i1}!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it's really true!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on now!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's really true...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.80,0:07:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell anyone the truth.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.18,0:07:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um, do you... do you know if...\Nif Kazuki-kun has a girl he likes?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.39,0:07:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-He was saying he thinks that's kinda creepy.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.40,0:07:50.95,Default,,10,10,0,,{\i1}And you know, when he watches romance shows on TV, \Nhe says they're totally made-up and boring.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.95,0:07:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I lied to my friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.82,0:07:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I lied to you, the person I love.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.37,0:08:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought it was better that way.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? You're fine with how things are?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.34,0:08:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.01,0:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll still love Kazuki forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.55,0:08:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even when he gets a girlfriend, marries, and has kids...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll keep this lie up as long as I live.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.69,0:08:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even when I'm old and alone,\NI'll love him until the day I die.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But on that day...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A card game?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.12,0:08:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's pretty fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.71,0:08:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you my Selector?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm Hanayo. Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.05,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The card... talked?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The card did what?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.06,0:09:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can't hear her, Kazuki? This card just...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.52,0:09:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't bother.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.56,0:09:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only Selectors can hear our voices.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.69,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}S-Selector...?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.78,0:09:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My wish can come true?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.32,0:09:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right. Whether you believe that or not is up to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have a wish, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.09,0:09:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've got nothing to lose. Go ahead and tell me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.38,0:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... love Kazu...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.26,0:09:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.84,0:09:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... love Kazuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.01,0:09:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kazuki? You mean your brother?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.57,0:09:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love Kazuki... I love Kazuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.70,0:09:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.32,0:10:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love Kazuki! I love him... I love him...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.41,0:10:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love him!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.33,0:10:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know this isn't right...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know it'll never be allowed!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.84,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I want to be with him!\NI want to be with Kazuki forever!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.47,0:10:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... I want to be Kazuki's...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.89,0:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to be his girlfriend!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.93,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, let's make it happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll make that wish come true.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So your wish was...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really doing my best...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,being straightforward.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Straightforward in my efforts.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Straightforward in being hurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Straightforward in hurting others.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.76,0:11:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time I was able to\Ntell someone how I truly felt.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the first, Hanayo-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.56,0:11:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... Hanayo-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.69,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I get to be with you,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't care if I'd get hurt,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,if the entire world were against me,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,or if I'd lose everything else in the process.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't been back since lunch.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.81,0:11:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty creepy...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A wish...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A wish you want to make come true,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.92,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}even if it means hurting yourself or hurting someone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.38,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time we meet, I'll be a new Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be Kazuki's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.01,0:12:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A feeling as straightforward as hers can't be numbed.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.95,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have a wish.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what we are about.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.75,0:12:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.80,0:13:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.47,0:13:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you lonely, Ruu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.02,0:13:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Hitoe and Yuzuki\Naren't your friends anymore?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tama is still your friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Battle...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.19,0:13:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we don't battle... we'll always be friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.78,0:13:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.16,0:13:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like having battles...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.95,0:13:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.21,0:13:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Tama.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruu!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.68,0:13:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitoe, why are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you remember me now?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.98,0:13:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruu!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitoe has a LRIG!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.40,0:14:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,LRIG?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... a Selector, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.57,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please battle me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.66,0:14:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be... You've become a Selector again?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.00,0:14:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please battle me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.92,0:14:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No—why?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.30,0:14:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I'm not battling anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So you say, but you're still taking Tama with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.23,0:14:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess that can't be helped, though.\NYou guys are really close after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.27,0:14:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.61,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, why not do a favor for a former friend of yours?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.95,0:14:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Yuzuki?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.96,0:15:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see! Well, not really, I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.84,0:15:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... a LRIG?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be real...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't... that can't be...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very much real.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That scrunchie!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the three of us have met again.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.15,0:15:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels pretty weird, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.53,0:15:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.87,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.07,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a lot to talk about,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but before that...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Battle Hitoe.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.08,0:15:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! I can't do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for Hitoe's sake.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.05,0:15:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for Hitoe's wish, and for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My wish...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Ruuko.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.76,0:16:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,For Hitoe and you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.99,0:16:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.58,0:16:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.58,0:16:23.46,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.31,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitoe... Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama! Grow!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.82,0:16:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Yuzuki! What happened?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I won my battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And my wish was approved.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.67,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your final attack, and your final oath.\NWe'll say it together.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, let's say it together.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.69,0:17:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I accept...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.11,0:17:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... accept!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Laws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.90,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Laws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.03,0:17:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new Eternal Girl will be born!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.03,0:17:40.03,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new Eternal Girl will be born!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Adamasphere!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.58,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Adamasphere!
