Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the Yuzuki now is...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.03,0:18:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-san... became Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.37,0:18:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When a girl's wish is approved, she becomes an Eternal Girl
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.12,0:18:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and gains the power to make wishes come true.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.67,0:18:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the one granting the wish...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the drawing I made in pre-school.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.19,0:18:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the princess.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The black scribble next to her...\NYou know who that is?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the prince in this drawing.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I wanted to be your bride.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.21,0:19:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But they told me that was a bad thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to blot it out, again and again.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.51,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I painted it over as thoroughly as I could.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.51,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But it didn't work.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.81,0:19:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Blot it out"...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.77,0:19:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I couldn't blot out my feelings, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you too.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.45,0:19:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I love you too, Yuzuki. I love you!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.25,0:19:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've loved you for so long...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.50,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we're family. I knew it wouldn't be allowed.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I lied to myself all this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.92,0:20:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried not to notice my feelings!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.30,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't care what happens anymore. I don't care what the others think!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.22,0:20:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind losing everything and leaving\Neveryone else behind as long as we're together!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.39,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Yuzuki! I love you! I love you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.53,0:20:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I... love you too, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.87,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The wish...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,came true.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.54,0:20:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That... that can't be!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.17,0:20:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The LRIG... grants the wish?
